\emph{Felis silvestris catus}; \emph{Capra hircus} vs \emph{Capra
aegagrus hircus}; \emph{Bos indicus} vs \emph{Bos taurus indicus}).
\item \strong{Taxonomic splits} — \emph{Alces americanus}, sometimes split
from \emph{A. alces}.
\item \strong{Hybrids} — e.g. \emph{Clanga clanga} × \emph{pomarina},
introgressed \emph{Ovis} entries.
\item \strong{Genus-only entries} — species recorded only to genus level
